description: Approval of reserved matters for Phase 3, pursuant to Condition 3 (i-iii) relating to Design of the Buildings, External Appearance and Landscaping, of outline approval of DC/09/72554, as amended by planning permission DC/10/752670 dated 29 September 2010 and DC/10/75395 dated 11 November 2010 for the development of the Heathside and Lethbridge Estates, Blackheath Hill and Lewisham Road SE10, to provide (Phases 2-6) for up to 512 square metres of retail floorspace, 768 square metres of community floorspace, an energy centre and 1054 residential units in buildings ranging from 3 to 17 storeys in height, together with car and cycle parking, associated highway infrastructure, public realm works and provision of open space.
